---
import HeadingLarge from "@components/HeadingLarge.astro";
import Text from "@components/Text.astro";
import View from "@components/View.astro";
import Group from "@components/Group.astro";
import { Layout } from "@layouts";
import Image from "@components/Image.astro";
import Heading from "@components/Heading.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Starboard | Jonathon Toon | Software Designer, Product Leader"
  description="Jonathon Toon is a versatile software designer and product leader based in Aotearoa New Zealand."
  keywords="design, software, product, fractional, leadership, new zealand, aotearoa, technology, typescript, start ups, engineering, mentorship, coaching, adplist"
  twitterHandle="@jonathontoon"
  canonicalUrl="https://www.jonathontoon.com/"
  ogImage="/images/og-image.png"
>
  <Group>
    <HeadingLarge class="px-2">Starboard</HeadingLarge>
    <Text class="px-2">
      Starboard is a New Zealand-based maritime intelligence platform that
      enables you to monitor vessel activity in real-time, whether you're
      protecting marine ecosystems, securing borders, or combating illegal
      fishing.
    </Text>
    <Text class="px-2">
      Developed alongside government users across New Zealand, Australia, and
      the Pacific, the platform processes over 4,000 vessel positions per
      second, giving you the comprehensive maritime surveillance capabilities
      needed to make informed decisions and take swift action.
    </Text>
    <Text class="px-2">
      In a part-time engagement I collaborated with Starboard's Chief of Product
      and Chief of Marketing to lead the complete redesign and development of
      their web experience, helping organizations better discover their
      solutions.
    </Text>
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <View class="px-2">
      <View class="h-px w-full bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-700" />
    </View>
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Heading class="px-2">Website Redesign</Heading>
    <Text class="px-2">
      Government agencies and maritime organizations were struggling to discover
      Starboard's surveillance capabilities through their outdated website,
      making it difficult for teams protecting marine ecosystems to find the
      intelligence tools they needed.
    </Text>
    <Text class="px-2">
      We conducted a comprehensive content audit and sitemap restructure based
      on sales and onboarding data, making it easier for government officials
      and researchers to quickly find case studies, technical documentation, and
      the specific maritime intelligence solutions relevant to their missions.
    </Text>
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-one.png"
      alt="Homepage design showcasing maritime surveillance expertise and global reach."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-two.png"
      alt="Solutions page highlighting real-time vessel tracking and analytics capabilities."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Text class="px-2">
      I designed and built 20+ pages on Webflow, along with migrating 100+
      articles, ensuring prospects could easily access relevant case studies,
      technical documentation, and solution details for their specific maritime
      challenges.
    </Text>
    <Text class="px-2">
      The final result was created in 3 months. Providing clearer product
      positioning, and an improved browsing experience that enable officials and
      maritime researchers to quickly understand how Starboard's intelligence
      platform could support their conservation and security missions.
    </Text>
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-three.png"
      alt="Resource center design organizing maritime intelligence insights and case studies."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-four.png"
      alt="About page emphasizing team expertise and company mission in ocean protection."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
  </Group>
</Layout>
